{"word":"G3377 - μηνύω - mēnýō - may-noo'-o - Shew","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μηνύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mēnýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">may-noo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Shew</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காண்பி, அறிவி, சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. to disclose"},{"paragraph":"2. to declare, tell"},{"paragraph":"3. to indicate, intimate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from the same base as <a href=\"#/G3145 - μασσάομαι - massáomai - mas-sah'-om-ahee/3145\">G3145</a> and <a href=\"#/G3415 - μνάομαι - mnáomai - mnah'-om-ahee/3415\">G3415</a> (that is, <b>&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>mao&#x0304;</b> [to <i>strive</i>]); to <i>disclose</i> (through the idea of mental <i>effort</i> and thus calling to <i>mind</i>), that is, <i>report</i>, <i>declare</i>, <i>intimate:</i> - shew, tell.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}